Package: adRutils
Title: Utility Functions for Data Analysis Workflows
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ana", "Boeriu",
           email = "your-email@domain",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utility functions supporting tidy data
    analysis workflows, including input validation, data cleaning,
    longitudinal coalescing, regression model batching, coefficient
    extraction, and random-effects meta-analysis. Designed to reduce
    boilerplate in research scripts and to work alongside domain-
    specific packages.
